Chonkiest lamp in the world 🌟

Gently tap to turn it on, tap again to change COLORS 💙💜❤️💛

Check out our friends over at The Chonkz 💕

Buy 1 Get 1 Free! 🔥🔥

Add both items to cart for automatic discount ✨
